    "story_name": "精灵们的森林 第18章 3-5 祝福之光",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "凯严被打倒后仍凭借其执念不肯放弃。\\n卢卡坚信世上众人皆可共存，\\n其刀上寄宿了重生之龙的力量，\\n终于成功击退凯严。但就在此时，\\n再次听到神秘声音的纳姆突发异变。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "呃……该死……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "好，能行！\\n卢卡，一口气干掉他！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "呃……唔唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "凯严，是你！\\n糟蹋了大伙一起\\n辛苦开拓的村子！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "伤害互相扶持的人们……\\n甚至夺走了他们的生命！\\n我绝对不会原谅你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "……\\n卢卡，汝……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "愚蠢至极……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你说啥！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "事到如今，竟然还在散播\\n那懦弱的思想。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "汝所盼的温馨和谐\\n终将招致堕落……\\n而堕落则将导致灭亡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "吾等正因为推崇\\n并满足于和谐，\\n才会遭到淘汰！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "老夫……吾等！\\n必须立于不败之地！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这家伙怎么回事……\\n竟然还能站起来？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "看着吧，看好了！\\n老夫贯穿天地开辟四海的攻击！\\n哈啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100034_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "领教老夫的六体了吗！\\n这才是老夫的强韧之巅！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "千锤百炼的肉体\\n与麒麟族的仙宝之力合二为一。\\n好厉害的招数……大家没事吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "可、可恶……\\n近距离狠狠挨了一下……\\n身体动不了了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "卢卡，你没事吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "该死……你等着！\\n我这就去帮你！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "你们两个不用担心……\\n我还能战……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "我怎么能输……\\n就算是为了那些和我一起\\n建立那个村子的伙伴们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "就算是为了那些\\n陪我实现梦想的家伙们！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉……\\n借你的刀一用。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "卢卡！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "那天我发誓，要创造一个\\n超越种族隔阂的世界！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "所以我无论如何都要\\n打倒那个来捣乱的家伙！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01",
                "100004_01",
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这道光是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "从那个方向来的！\\n有什么东西出现了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "那是……贞德！\\n但是没见过她这个样子啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210144_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贞德",
            "context": "卢卡，向你那清澈的魔力波动\\n和那高洁闪耀的灵魂\\n献上伟大祝福！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "这是什么情况？\\n身体里充满了力量！\\n好，这下能行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "唔噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "这、这股力量是……\\n呃……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "凯严",
            "context": "卢卡，汝本应“弱小”才对……\\n为何，为何会有这般力量！\\n唔呃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "——敌对反应彻底消失。\\n——那个男人似乎不在了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "是啊……\\n其实我控制了力道，\\n他一定还没死。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "马斯古拉的这把刀\\n不是用来夺命的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100032_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱姬希",
            "context": "卢卡，你还想着我……\\n你的这份心意，让我很开心！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "贞德……\\n是你把力量借给我的吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210144_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贞德",
            "context": "卢卡，多亏接触到你的心意，\\n我才得以驱除黑暗魔力。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210144_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "贞德",
            "context": "我扬此旌旗祈祷。\\n愿你和伙伴们的旅途\\n与光明同在……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "卢卡，要是没有你，\\n我早就……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "喂喂，尤蒂尔，\\n你又要说“谢谢” 了吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "都说了！别说这些见外的话！\\n咱们是哥们，我不是说了\\n帮你是理所当然的嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，即便如此我也要道谢。\\n谢谢你至今为止的帮助，\\n还有我今后将会需要的帮助。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "卢卡，谢谢你……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "好啦……\\n“不客气”，这样总行了吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "不过，听哥们道谢\\n其实也不错啊，嘿嘿！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100015_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "谢斯",
            "context": "呵呵，虽然有点夸张，\\n不过美好的友情\\n倒也不坏……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "嗯，尤蒂尔\\n身边有一群可靠的伙伴呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100042_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "迦道夫",
            "context": "好，暴风雪也停了，\\n我们重新向山顶进发吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊。各位，我们走！\\n席菈，拜托你继续带路了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100044_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "席菈",
            "context": "……\\n声……音……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "嗯？\\n席菈，你刚才说了什么吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "！\\n又来了？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "纳姆，怎么了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "跟刚才一样，\\n脑袋里有声音！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘的声音",
            "context": "（纳姆啊……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "到底是怎么回事嘛！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "神秘的声音",
            "context": "（我有言相告。\\n你接收便是……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "什么情况？\\n诶……什、什么！\\n这是什么啊！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_07"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "泽娜",
            "context": "纳姆，你怎么了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "好多东西……\\n涌进脑袋了……\\n不要啊，住手！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "脑、脑袋要裂开了！\\n不要啊！不要！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100007_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "不要啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_18_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}